values:
ahhh my crush is getting bigger. Well I don't know if you'd call it a crush, I mean we've been seeing eachother off and on for like 2 years now, but I actually like him this time, like really like him.

Of course it's just my luck that he might be moving with his brother to Japan in April for about a year. God damnit.

Buuuuut I found out what Bjork's tattoo on her arm means.

So wednesday was amazing. The AmeriKan Made show at the House of Blues was fun, and theeennnn Hannah and I decided to go to Errica and Paul's house in Orange and we somehow managed to get inside one of those giant inflatable snow globes with the snowmen inside of them and have a wrestling match in our underwear. It was so much fucking fun at the time, but then the next morning we looked through the pictures and well, we look fucking retarded to say the least.

But while we were still at the House of Blues they gave us 4 free tickets to go see and evening with John Kricfalusi (the creator of Ren and Stimpy). It was so cool! They played never before seen episodes of Ren and Stimpy and shit, oh man it was fun, until the question and answer part, people ask the stupidest questions.

...and I have a valentine tehehe.
But too bad I'm grounded because of the little snowman escapade instead of going home and going to school the next day.

I want to get druuuunk...
and then really stoned the next morning when I'm all hung over and watching The Simpsons.
Yeah, that'd be sweet.

I'm soooooo upset. It's kindof like to the point that I'm so mad and I'm freaking out so much that all I can do is laugh about it or else I might go crazy.

All I want to do is get the hell out of this stupid house and go to the Galaxy to see The Starvations play their last show. Ugh. Okay, I'm done venting. I need a beer.

OMG! alcohol at Disneyland. AND LAURA AND I ARE GOING AGAIN TOMORROW! hahaha I'm obsessed.

so i found a crap load of pictures from like 2 or 3 years ago, I'm wayyy excited, theres like a million. here's a few but I don't know how to make it so they show up on another page, I'm computer illiterate. yeah, my hair used to be really long we all got wayyy too drunk and convinced John to take shots of Wesson Oil. oops. this picture got me through so many bad days haha, I used to have it up on my wall. so I wake up the next morning around 7:30, 8, and John's gone, but he left this note "Natassia and Co. ..." hahaha ahhh yes the SS Victory and the Insta Mohawk. fuck man, we used to be so much more fun, what the hell happened to us? ^^oh yeah I forgot, we all became just a little emo.^^^

This weekend was okay,friday went to Tara's while everyone was still at school then we went to Noise Attack practice and got waayyy stoned at Orbits, and then went back and partied with my sister. I forgot to call Laura :( I have to stop smoking pot. Got drunk, Andy broke something, and I sprayed Alex and myself with a fire extinguisher on accident because I wanted to write my name on the wall with it. That was totally lame, I still don't think I got all the shit out of my throat.
and then.. there was saturday, the most amazing night ever! I saw Odd Project with Brent, saw Jenny, Terri and Larry, I haven't seen them in forever... 
uhhh I saw Eddie and Jon, he was so suprised to see me haha his face when he saw me was classic. There was this cool band wth a banjo and like a stand up bass, but it was like a chello too, I forgot what they were called.

MATT LAMB IS HOTTER THAN EVER!

I can still remember the first time I saw him and had to run back home to tell everyone I just saw the hottest guy ever at the Westminster mall, and of course everyone already knew who he was.
but yea, THEN we went to Sonics, it was amazing. I wish there was one closer than Anaheim.
aaaaand then me and Andy, Jaclyn, Nick and Sarah went to Jon's birthday thing in Wesminster at some chicks house, but it was boring.
I don't like Sarah. she sucks. but I'm probably just jealous.
haha okay, well that's about it.
I'm off to go paint my livingroom.

I'm so freaking excited.
